Detailed Description

A node structure that will be gathered into a list. 

 // Create two node and link to each other.
 Node node1(NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
 Node node2(node1, node1, NULL, NULL, NULL);
 node1.setPrevPtr(node2);
 node1.serNextPtr(node2);
 
 // Set data for node1.
 int a = 2011;
 node1.setDataPtr(&a);
